###Configuring kubernetes service accunt to Assume an IAM Role

## Configuring Bucket Policy

cat >S3BucketAccess.json <<EOF
{
    "Version": "2012-10-17",
    "Statement": [
        {
            "Effect": "Allow",
            "Action": "s3:GetObject",
            "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::my-pod-secrets-bucket"
        }
    ]
}
EOF
